<BaseLayout>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        Effective date: February 24, 2026<br>
        <br>
        This Privacy Policy explains how EddiesGames (“we”, “us”) collects and uses information when you visit our website and play our browser games.<br>
        <br>
        What we collect<br>
        <br>
        Information you provide:<br>
        Right now, we don’t require accounts and we don’t ask you to submit personal information to play.<br>
        <br>
        Automatically collected information:<br>
        Like most websites, we (and our service providers) may collect basic technical data such as:<br>
        IP address<br>
        browser and device type<br>
        pages visited and time spent approximate location (derived from IP)<br>
        general performance/diagnostic data (e.g., errors)<br>
        <br>
        This is typically collected via standard server logs and analytics tools.<br>
        <br>
        Cookies and similar technologies<br>
        <br>
        We may use cookies and similar technologies for:<br>
        basic site functionality<br>
        analytics (understanding what pages/games people use)<br>
        advertising (if/when ads are enabled)<br>
        See our Cookie Policy for details.<br>
        <br>
        Advertising<br>
        If we run ads, third-party ad networks may use cookies or similar technologies to show ads and measure performance. Those providers may collect information about your visit to this and other sites.<br>
        <br>
        Analytics<br>
        We may use analytics tools (including privacy-friendly options) to understand traffic and improve the site. Analytics may involve cookies or similar technologies.<br>
        <br>
        How we use information<br>
        We use information to:<br>
        operate and maintain the site<br>
        improve games and site performance<br>
        troubleshoot bugs and prevent abuse<br>
        measure traffic and content performance<br>
        (if enabled) serve and measure advertising<br>
        <br>
        Data retention<br>
        We retain information only as long as needed for the purposes above, including security and troubleshooting. Server logs are typically kept for a limited period.<br>
        <br>
        Children’s privacy<br>
        This site is intended for a general audience. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you believe a child has provided personal data, contact us and we will take appropriate steps.<br>
        <br>
        Security<br>
        No website is perfectly secure, but we use reasonable measures to protect information and reduce risk.<br>
        <br>
        International visitors<br>
        If you access the site from outside the United States, your information may be processed in other countries where our hosting/analytics providers operate.<br>
        <br>
        Changes to this policy<br>
        We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.<br>
        <br>
        Contact: <a href="mailto:eddie@eddiesgames.xyz">eddie@eddiesgames.xyz</a>
</BaseLayout>